mily:等线&quot;&gt;（二）供货与售后&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0;line-height: 120%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(51,112,255);font-size:15px&quot;&gt;•&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-variant-emoji: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Arial;line-height:120%;font-size:15px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;供货说明：河南郑州工厂直发，主力型号现货充足，&lt;/span&gt;2&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;天内发货，支持全国物流配送，批量采购（&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial&quot;&gt;≥5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;台）享&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial&quot;&gt;8-9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;折优惠。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0;line-height: 120%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(51,112,255);font-size:15px&quot;&gt;•&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-variant-emoji: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Arial;line-height:120%;font-size:15px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;定制服务：支持定制喷砂机罐体容积、空压机功率&lt;/span&gt;/&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;排气量，适配特殊作业场景需求。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0;line-height: 120%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(51,112,255);font-size:15px&quot;&gt;•&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-variant-emoji: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Arial;line-height:120%;font-size:15px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;售后保障：&lt;/span&gt;1&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;年整机质保，终身维护，易损件（喷嘴、胶管、滤芯）现货供应，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial&quot;&gt;48&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;小时上门维修，提供专业施工技术指导。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 21px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0;line-height: 120%&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Arial;line-height:120%;font-size:21px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;五、维护保养建议&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0;line-height: 120%&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Arial;line-height:120%;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;（一）喷砂机保养&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0;line-height: 120%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(51,112,255);font-size:15px&quot;&gt;•&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-variant-emoji: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Arial;line-height:120%;font-size:15px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;日常检查：每次作业前清理罐体、管路残留磨料，检查喷嘴磨损情况（磨损超&lt;/span&gt;1/3&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;及时更换）、液压管路是否泄漏、接头是否松动。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0;line-height: 120%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(51,112,255);font-size:15px&quot;&gt;•&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-variant-emoji: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Arial;line-height:120%;font-size:15px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;定期保养：每&lt;/span&gt;50&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;小时润滑喷枪、阀门部件，每&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial&quot;&gt;200&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;小时更换密封件，检查罐体焊缝有无泄漏，避免安全隐患。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0;line-height: 120%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(51,112,255);font-size:15px&quot;&gt;•&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-variant-emoji: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Arial;line-height:120%;font-size:15px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;专项保养：湿式机型定期清理水循环系统，更换过滤棉，避免堵枪；长期停用前，清理设备内残留磨料，做好防锈处理。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0;line-height: 120%&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Arial;line-height:120%;font-size:20px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;（二）空压机保养&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0;line-height: 120%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(51,112,255);font-size:15px&quot;&gt;•&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-variant-emoji: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Arial;line-height:120%;font-size:15px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;定期换件：每&lt;/span&gt;500&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;小时更换机油、机油滤芯，每&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial&quot;&gt;1000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;小时更换空气滤芯、油气分离器，保障运行效率。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0;line-height: 120%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(51,112,255);font-size:15px&quot;&gt;•&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-variant-emoji: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Arial;line-height:120%;font-size:15px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;日常清理：定期清理冷却器灰尘，检查皮带松紧度（工频款），永磁变频款无需皮带维护。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 0;line-height: 120%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Arial;color:rgb(51,112,255);font-size:15px&quot;&gt;•&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-size-adjust: none;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-variant-emoji: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Arial;line-height:120%;font-size:15px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;安全校验：储气罐每月排水，安全阀、压力表每&lt;/span&gt;6&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:等线&quot;&gt;个月校验一次，确保设备运行安全。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;');
